query:
SELECT
                t.id AS id,
                t.tag AS tag,
                bt.bike_id AS bike_id
            FROM
                "Tag" AS t
                    INNER JOIN
                "BikeTag" as bt ON bt.tag_id = t.id
            WHERE
                (t.id = $1 OR $1 IS NULL)
                AND (t.tag = $2 OR $2 IS NULL)
                AND (bt.bike_id = $3 OR $3 IS NULL)
            ORDER BY tag
